        <item>
            <title>3.1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 14:42:56 +0800</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/sj719045032/claude-statistics</link>
            <sparkle:version>3.1.1</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New</h2>
<ul>
<li>Unified Claude OAuth and subscription-extension account switching in one menu.</li>
<li>Fixed GLM/subscription selections so the Usage chip shows the active subscription account instead of the Claude email.</li>
<li>Restored the Claude Add Account entry while GLM and other subscription plugins are installed.</li>
<li>Improved account removal behavior for the last Claude OAuth account.</li>
</ul>
<h2>中文</h2>
<ul>
<li>统一 Claude OAuth 与订阅扩展账号切换入口，GLM 不再使用另一套交互。</li>
<li>修复切到 GLM/订阅账号后 Usage 顶部仍显示 Claude 邮箱的问题，现在显示当前订阅账号。</li>
<li>安装 GLM 等订阅插件后仍可直接添加 Claude 账号。</li>
<li>改进删除最后一个 Claude OAuth 账号时的退出登录清理逻辑。</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
